data.description: Welcome home, to this completely remodeled 4 bedroom 2 bathroom ranch style home located in La Salle. The 2024 remodel is currently in progress! Updated pictures will be uploaded upon completion. The scope of the current remodel shall include the following: New interior plumbing and venting will be installed soon. Once the plumbing work is finished then new dry wall will be installed on the affected basement walls. Once the walls are complete then, new flooring and baseboards will be installed in the basement. New floor outlets will be installed on the main level, new GFI outlets throughout the house, new electrical wiring inside the garage, and a new furnace gas line. Updates from the 2022 remodel included: new main floor windows, new interior paint, new laminate flooring on the main floor, completely remodeled kitchen, both bathrooms and finished basement. 2016 remodel included: a new roof, exterior paint, landscaping, and fencing. This home has a large, 2 car detached garage that could also be used as a workshop. Huge driveway- ideal for a basketball court and additional off street parking for your boat and RV. No HOA! Big backyard includes- 3 raised gardening beds, and a storage shed. Great location on a quiet street. The home backs to open space on one side and is diagonally across from a corn field on the front side of the home. Located within walking distance to downtown La Salle including restaurants, parks and recreation. Book your showing today and don't let this one get away.  Sellers would also like to include the following items with a full price offer: Clothes washer, clothes dryer, upstairs brown sectional couch, downstairs grey sectional couch, coffee table, master bedroom queen bed frame entertainment center with built in heater, 3 AC window units, kitchen table and chairs, backyard fire pit, trampoline, and the above ground swimming pool.
